
  CREATE TABLE "THH_C4C"."CLAIM_REVIEW"
   (	"CLAIM_REVIEW_ID" NUMBER(19,0),
	"CREATION_DATE" DATE DEFAULT sysdate NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"OBJECT_STATE" NUMBER(1,0),
	"ENABLE_CLAIM_REVIEW" NUMBER(1,0),
	"CLAIM_SERVICE_START_DATE" DATE,
	"CLAIM_SERVICE_END_DATE" DATE,
	"CLAIM_RECEIPT_START_DATE" DATE,
	"CLAIM_RECEIPT_END_DATE" DATE,
	"CLAIM_TYPE" NUMBER(1,0),
	"REQUESTING_USER" VARCHAR2(50),
	"REVIEW_REASON_DESCRIPTION" VARCHAR2(50),
	"CLAIM_REVIEW_REASON" VARCHAR2(50),
	"PROVIDER_ID" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	 CHECK (object_state in (1,2)) ENABLE,
	 CHECK (enable_claim_review in (0,1)) ENABLE,
	 CHECK (claim_type in (1,2)) ENABLE,
	 PRIMARY KEY ("CLAIM_REVIEW_ID")
  USING INDEX PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"  ENABLE,
	 CONSTRAINT "FK_CLAIM_REVIEW_PROVIDER_ID" FOREIGN KEY ("PROVIDER_ID")
	  REFERENCES "THH_C4C"."T_USR" ("PRV_ID") ENABLE
   ) SEGMENT CREATION IMMEDIATE
  PCTFREE 10 PCTUSED 40 INITRANS 1 MAXTRANS 255
 NOCOMPRESS LOGGING
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"


  CREATE TABLE "THH_C4C"."CLINICALDATA_ASSN"
   (	"OBJECTID" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"CLINICALDATADEF" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,

	 UNIQUE ("UNIVERSALID")

	 CONSTRAINT "UK_CLINICALDATA_ASSN" UNIQUE ("AFFILIATION_TYPE", "TYPE", "SUBTYPE1", "SUBTYPE2", "SUBTYPE3")
  USING INDEX PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"  ENABLE,
	 CONSTRAINT "FK_CLINICALDATADEF" FOREIGN KEY ("CLINICALDATADEF")

	 CONSTRAINT "FK_LAS_ACT_BY" FOREIGN KEY ("LAS_ACT_BY")
	  REFERENCES "THH_C4C"."T_USR" ("USR_ID") ENABLE
   ) SEGMENT CREATION DEFERRED
  PCTFREE 10 PCTUSED 40 INITRANS 1 MAXTRANS 255
 NOCOMPRESS LOGGING
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"

  CREATE TABLE "THH_C4C"."INSTRUCTION_CARD"
   (	"OBJECTID" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"UNIVERSALID" VARCHAR2(255) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"NAME" VARCHAR2(255) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"CREATED_DATE" DATE DEFAULT sysdate NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"MODIFIED_DATE" DATE DEFAULT sysdate NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"CREATED_BY" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"MODIFIED_BY" NUMBER(19,0) NOT NULL ENABLE,
	"TEXT" CLOB,
	"ATTACHMENT_ID" NUMBER(19,0),
	 PRIMARY KEY ("OBJECTID")
  USING INDEX PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"  ENABLE,
	 CONSTRAINT "UNIVERSALID_UN" UNIQUE ("UNIVERSALID")
  USING INDEX PCTFREE 10 INITRANS 2 MAXTRANS 255 COMPUTE STATISTICS
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"  ENABLE,
	 FOREIGN KEY ("CREATED_BY")
	  REFERENCES "THH_C4C"."T_USR" ("USR_ID") ENABLE,
	 FOREIGN KEY ("MODIFIED_BY")
	  REFERENCES "THH_C4C"."T_USR" ("USR_ID") ENABLE,
	 FOREIGN KEY ("ATTACHMENT_ID")
	  REFERENCES "THH_C4C"."T_FIL" ("FILE_ID") ENABLE
   ) SEGMENT CREATION IMMEDIATE
  PCTFREE 10 PCTUSED 40 INITRANS 1 MAXTRANS 255
 NOCOMPRESS LOGGING
  STORAGE(INITIAL 65536 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0 FREELISTS 1 FREELIST GROUPS 1
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT)
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C"
 LOB ("TEXT") STORE AS SECUREFILE (
  TABLESPACE "THHC4C" ENABLE STORAGE IN ROW CHUNK 8192
  NOCACHE LOGGING  NOCOMPRESS  KEEP_DUPLICATES
  STORAGE(INITIAL 106496 NEXT 1048576 MINEXTENTS 1 MAXEXTENTS 2147483645
  PCTINCREASE 0
  BUFFER_POOL DEFAULT FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT CELL_FLASH_CACHE DEFAULT))

  CREATE OR REPLACE EDITIONABLE FUNCTION "THH_C4C"."REVERSE_STR"
(
  par_str_direct IN VARCHAR2
)
RETURN
  VARCHAR2
DETERMINISTIC
AS

 ret_str_reverse VARCHAR2(4000) := NULL;

BEGIN

  FOR char_idx IN REVERSE 1..nvl(length(par_str_direct), 0) LOOP

    ret_str_reverse := ret_str_reverse || substr(par_str_direct, char_idx, 1);

  END LOOP;

  RETURN ret_str_reverse;

END reverse_str;
